OL,6,FBlue Islands' workers were only
OL,7,Fofficially told of the airline's
OL,8,Fcollapse by email 10 minutes before a
OL,9,Fpublic media release stating they had
OL,10,Fceased trading.
OL,12,FThe message from Chief Executive
OL,13,FOfficer Rob Veron, marked as "company
OL,14,Fconfidential" and since leaked to ITV
OL,15,FNews, was received by staff at 9:43pm
OL,16,Fon Friday.
