OL,6,FIn it, he writes: "I am shocked and
OL,7,Fsaddened beyond words to be sending
OL,8,Fthis message, just as I know you will
OL,9,Fbe shocked and saddened to receive and
OL,10,Fread it.
OL,12,F"I'm truly sorry that our airline
OL,13,Fwhich we have all worked so hard to
OL,14,Fbuild has, as of this evening, likely
OL,15,Ftaken its final flight."
OL,17,FHe adds that industry-wide supply
OL,18,Fissues with maintenance for its ATR
OL,19,Faircraft have been "impacting our
OL,20,Fbusiness severely".
