OL,6,FMr Veron claims that the Ports of
OL,7,FJersey and the Government of Jersey
OL,8,F"provided funding and legally-backed
OL,9,Fassurances" which was withdrawn by the
OL,10,FGovernment late on Friday afternoon.
OL,12,FHe explains: "This was not an outcome
OL,13,Fthat we had expected, nor could we
OL,14,Fpossibly have seen that this
OL,15,Fafternoon's events would result in
OL,16,Fmatters deteriorating as quickly as
OL,17,Fthey have."
OL,19,FMr Veron has made no public comment
OL,20,Fsince the announcement, despite
OL,21,Frepeated requests from ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/13
