OL,6,FHowever, sources have told ITV News
OL,7,Fthat the Government of Jersey had been
OL,8,Fpropping up Blue Islands for millions
OL,9,Fof pounds and could no longer justify
OL,10,Fthe business case for continuing to
OL,11,Ffund them through the use of
OL,12,Ftaxpayers' money.
OL,14,FAround 100 Blue Islands' staff are set
OL,15,Fto lose their jobs, with Loganair and
OL,16,FAurigny offering extra flights to help
OL,17,Fdisplaced passengers get home.
