OL,6,FLoganair has also been drafted in to
OL,7,Fsecure lifeline routes between the
OL,8,FChannel Islands and the UK, with hopes
OL,9,Fthat some Blue Islands' staff can be
OL,10,Ftaken on as part of the new operation.
OL,12,FThe full email from Blue Islands' CEO
OL,13,FRob Veron to staff on Friday evening:
