OL,6,F** The following update is company
OL,7,Fconfidential and must not be forwarded
OL,8,Foutside the company. A separate press
OL,9,Fstatement has been prepared for public
OL,10,Frelease. **
OL,12,FIt is with the deepest sadness that I
OL,13,Fam writing to say that Blue Islands
OL,14,Fhas suspended operations with
OL,15,Fimmediate effect this evening. We will
OL,16,Fproceed to seek advice in the coming
OL,17,Fdays.
