OL,6,FThroughout this time, Ports of Jersey
OL,7,Fand the Government of Jersey has
OL,8,Fsupported the airline and has provided
OL,9,Ffunding and legally-backed assurances
OL,10,Fwhich have enabled us to keep Blue
OL,11,FIslands flying and work towards a
OL,12,Fsecure long-term future for everyone,
OL,13,Fnot least for the critical
OL,14,Fconnectivity that we have worked so
OL,15,Fhard to provide for the island of
OL,16,FJersey and its residents.
OL,18,FAt its heart Blue Islands has always
OL,19,Fsought to serve its island community.
