OL,6,FThe support provided to date by Ports
OL,7,Fof Jersey and the Government of
OL,8,FJersey, together with our constructive
OL,9,Fdiscussions, had given us much hope
OL,10,Falong that path.
OL,12,FWe were notified very late this
OL,13,Fafternoon that Government of Jersey
OL,14,Fhave withdrawn that support.
OL,16,FWe have therefore taken the difficult
OL,17,Fdecision to cancel all Blue Islands
OL,18,Fflights.
