OL,6,FPassengers expecting to fly should not
OL,7,Fgo to the airport unless they have
OL,8,Fmade alternative travel arrangements
OL,9,Fwith another airline. Please do not
OL,10,Fattend the office at this time.
OL,12,FIt is not through absence of effort
OL,13,Fand willpower in the face of adversity
OL,14,Fthat we've reached this position - far
OL,15,Ffrom it.
OL,17,FIt is simply a reflection that today's
OL,18,Fsudden and unexpected withdrawal of
OL,19,Fsupport has led to the conclusion that
OL,20,Fwe cannot continue to fly.
