OL,6,FIt saddens me beyond words that all I
OL,7,Fcan now do is extend our grateful
OL,8,Fthanks to you for all of your hard
OL,9,Fwork and efforts, and indeed to all of
OL,10,Four passengers for their custom over
OL,11,Fthe last 26 years.
OL,13,FWe will do all that we can to support
OL,14,Fyou, including putting arrangements in
OL,15,Fplace to provide references and
OL,16,Ftraining records to our air crew and
OL,17,Fteam members to help expedite the
OL,18,Fsearch for employment with other
OL,19,Fairlines or elsewhere.
